 from Camden Town - walking along the canal walk - which was prohibited. But if you saw them and of course there would be a clash. You knew what a clash meant don't you? Stone throwing. There would - there could be that. Or some would come the other way f
rom Marylebone. In a - in a way you were jealously guarding your territory see. But otherwise no, there was no -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4738731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2248743\charrsid13067595 You say it was out of bounds anyway, you shouldn't have been there?
