\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8675640 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2248743\charrsid13067595 Yes, well of course out of bounds to a youngster. No. He'd slide
 in just the same, my - I could always gain admittance into the zoo. Never any task for me. In fact - as soon as I go through the bushes with all innocence I would seek what pleasures what was in my mind. That was nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4738731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2248743\charrsid13067595 There were lots of things going on around you?
