Well of course sport - dominated. I used to love history. I was very good at writing, printing, map drawing, very good. In fact I was so good with the p
en - that I would - when I was thirteen I would copy every class exam - of - headmaster's dossier, I'd sit in the big hall and do it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4738731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2248743\charrsid13067595 Would you have gone on if you could have stayed at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8675640 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2248743\charrsid13067595 No. No, I was - impatient to get out into the big world.
